snippet.title: Pigsaw
snippet.description:
Play it here!
https://achebit.itch.io/pigsaw

Pigsaw is a bloody fever dream of first person shooter, stealth, survival horror, and immersive sim light. You are trapped in a nightmarish human abattoir, use whatever is at your disposal and do whatever is neccassary to stay alive and escape. The Butchers are relentless, expect no mercy and give none in return.
